description.standard:
Accept credit cards and run your business on the go and in store with Square Register. Process Visa, MasterCard, Discover and American Express, pay just 2.75% per swipe, and access your funds in 1-2 business days. No monthly fees, commitments, or surprises.

HOW IT WORKS
1. Download Square Register.
2. Sign up and request your free Square Reader.
3. Plug in your Square Reader and start taking payments.

2.75% PER SWIPE
Swipe $100, see $97.25 in your bank account. Accept Visa, MasterCard, Discover, and American Express at the same rate.

NEXT-DAY DEPOSITS
Square deposits payments into your bank account in 1-2 business days.

FREE SECURE CARD READER
Request your free Square Reader at sign-up. Credit card information is encrypted at swipe.

COMPLETE POINT OF SALE
Transform an iPad into a complete point of sale. Square Register for iPad works with receipt printers, kitchen ticket printers, cash drawers, and barcode scanners.

BACK OFFICE TOOLS
Sign in to your web dashboard to access all your business data plus tools to help you make sense of it.

FREE ONLINE STORE
Set up your online store free in Square Market. Accept orders for shipping and in-person pickup. 

FEATURES
Square Register has everything you need to start, run and grow your business from your iPhone, iPod touch, or iPad. Get the latest in point of sale features with app updates.
- Swipe or key in all major credit cards
- Record cash, gift cards, and other forms of tender
- Accept and manage pickup orders
- Customize your products with photos, names, and prices
- Customers sign and tip right on your device
- Send receipts via email or text message
- Apply discounts, create order modifiers, issue refunds
- Access real-time sales data and complete sales history

iPad only
- Sync hardware with Square Register for iPad
- Reconcile your cash drawer
- Print receipts and kitchen tickets 
- Connect barcode scanner
- Set employee logins and permissions
